{"tid":1046440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港澳台企業憂失外商資格","createTime":"2019-03-04T08:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T00:03:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2d9c01e5ac08a014f362c0ec9209824e51d72c38","tid":1046440,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:58:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190304/20625588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F20625588&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4MdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=dea01984\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F20625588&h=c2748619\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190304/20625588</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港澳台企業憂失外商資格<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190304/large/04la3p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190304%2Flarge%2F04la3p4.jpg&h=8022c645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬逢國<br />\n<br />\n【外商投資法出台】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】為安撫美國以消弭貿易戰而火速出爐的《外商投資法（草案）》，將於今次全國人大會議審議並料獲通過。新法將回應西方跨國企業近年對中國營商環境的抱怨，包括加強保護知識產權，規定政府不能利用「行政手段」強制外商轉讓技術等，但港澳台投資者是否一如現行法例繼續被視為「外商」享有外商待遇仍未明朗，惹港區人大代表關注。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：汪洋︰要旗幟鮮明反港獨 重提高度自治 圖減國際憂慮<br />\n<br />\n立法過程不到三個月<br />\n<br />\n港區人大代表團團長馬逢國表示，昨與全國人大常委會副秘書長信春鷹會面時，已向對方反映香港商界的意見和憂慮。全國人大常委譚耀宗早前曾稱，港商現時透過CEPA，已享有《外商投資法》實施後的同等保障，相信國務院頒佈實施細則時，會列明港商同受《外商投資法》保障。<br />\n<br />\n《外商投資法》在去年12月23日首次提請全國人大常委會審議，今年1月30日再在常委會二審，火速交付明天開幕的全國人大會議期間審議並付諸通過，整個立法過程不到三個月。內地「第一財經」報道，代表普遍認為有需要適當說明，《草案》中所指的「外商」是否包括港澳台投資者。大陸海協會會長、全國人大外事委員會副主任張志軍認為，首先要明確這是涉外的而不是涉內的法，港澳台投資者從大原則應界定為「特殊內資」，解決港澳台人士的顧慮可以考慮在通過《外商投資法》後由國務院通過行政法規作說明，給港澳台企業定心丸。<br />\n<br />\n官方統計，2017年內地實際投入外資金額排名前十的國家和地區，香港和台灣分別第一和第三。《外商投資法》通過後，原有的《中外合資經營企業法》、《外資企業法》、《中外合作經營企業法》將被廢止，並設五年的過渡期，而之前法律對港澳台資一直以「外資」待遇處理。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘯軒  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n汪洋︰要旗幟鮮明反港獨  重提高度自治 圖減國際憂慮<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n李慧詩贏凱林賽再創歷史<br />\n<br />\n汪洋︰要旗幟鮮明反港獨 重提高度自治 圖減國際憂慮"},{"pid":"dbf2ea5ed1ac77354b4322e61ce0f2839da9ef86","tid":1046440,"uid":24140,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20190302/s00013/1551464623889/%e6%96%b0%e3%80%8a%e5%a4%96%e5%95%86%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e6%b3%95%e3%80%8b-%e7%84%a1%e7%b4%8d%e5%85%a5%e6%b8%af%e6%be%b3%e5%8f%b0-%e7%94%b0%e5%8c%97%e8%be%b0-%e6%87%89%e8%ac%9b%e6%98%8e%e6%b8%af%e9%9d%9e%e3%80%8c%e5%a4%96%e5%95%86%e3%80%8d%e4%bd%86%e5%8f%af%e4%ba%ab%e5%a4%96%e5%95%86%e5%be%85%e9%81%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20190302%2Fs00013%2F1551464623889%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e3%2580%258a%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%2595%2586%25e6%258a%2595%25e8%25b3%2587%25e6%25b3%2595%25e3%2580%258b-%25e7%2584%25a1%25e7%25b4%258d%25e5%2585%25a5%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%25be%25b3%25e5%258f%25b0-%25e7%2594%25b0%25e5%258c%2597%25e8%25be%25b0-%25e6%2587%2589%25e8%25ac%259b%25e6%2598%258e%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%259d%259e%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%2595%2586%25e3%2580%258d%25e4%25bd%2586%25e5%258f%25af%25e4%25ba%25ab%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%2595%2586%25e5%25be%2585%25e9%2581%2587&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4MdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=7083fab1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20190302%2Fs00013%2F1551464623889%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e3%2580%258a%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%2595%2586%25e6%258a%2595%25e8%25b3%2587%25e6%25b3%2595%25e3%2580%258b-%25e7%2584%25a1%25e7%25b4%258d%25e5%2585%25a5%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%25be%25b3%25e5%258f%25b0-%25e7%2594%25b0%25e5%258c%2597%25e8%25be%25b0-%25e6%2587%2589%25e8%25ac%259b%25e6%2598%258e%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%259d%259e%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%2595%2586%25e3%2580%258d%25e4%25bd%2586%25e5%258f%25af%25e4%25ba%25ab%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%2595%2586%25e5%25be%2585%25e9%2581%2587&h=201517c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20190302/s00013/1551464623889/%e6%96%b0%e3%80%8a%e5%a4%96%e5%95%86%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e6%b3%95%e3%80%8b-%e7%84%a1%e7%b4%8d%e5%85%a5%e6%b8%af%e6%be%b3%e5%8f%b0-%e7%94%b0%e5%8c%97%e8%be%b0-%e6%87%89%e8%ac%9b%e6%98%8e%e6%b8%af%e9%9d%9e%e3%80%8c%e5%a4%96%e5%95%86%e3%80%8d%e4%bd%86%e5%8f%af%e4%ba%ab%e5%a4%96%e5%95%86%e5%be%85%e9%81%87</a><br />\n<br />\n結果已出<br />\n港澳台一齊無份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係就支那係對美上讓步讓得好緊要<br />\n一係就準備劏港資台資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22905d9c9dd82c8511dd2e291c08859aefd539a0","tid":1046440,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:31:03.000Z","msg":"裡外不是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83ec32f2412c9b3ec9cb03620dae00d19e78a6e","tid":1046440,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:34:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">港澳台投資者從大原則應界定為「特殊內資」</span>，解決港澳台人士的顧慮可以考慮在通過《外商投資法》後由國務院通過行政法規作說明，給港澳台企業定心丸。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87750310b2d64d4fe9b45b24c7bfa6e74f86a44","tid":1046440,"uid":213846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d9c01e5ac08a014f362c0ec9209824e51d72c38","tid":1046440,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:58:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190304/20625588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F20625588&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4MdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=dea01984\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledail